title: Impulse Icon Pack v1.0.3 APK (Android)
description:
Sticking to only five main colours in the palette, Impulse takes a bold new step in design, focusing on colour, aesthetics and looking unique on your homescreen!

What does Impulse Include?
1050+ Uniquely Designed Icons, Cloud-Stored Wallpapers, a Unique Dashboard Application with Icon Request, Dynamic Calendar Support and much more!

Material (Android 6.0+ Marshmallow) Ready!
Includes icon glyphs to match the new Material Design introduced by Google for Android Lollipop. Also looks great on Material Wallpapers.

Quad HD Ready!
Each icon is crafted at 512x512px, then resized to 192x192px (XXXHDPI) to ensure no quality loss when viewed on any device.

Help me to grow this icon pack!Are you missing icons from your phone? Instead of rating poorly, feel free to send me an icon request from within the dashboard app and I will try to update this pack as soon as possible!
(Please keep in mind, there is already a huge queue of icon request emails, so I cannot guarantee your request will make it in the next update, but I will try my best!)

Beautify your screen!
Simply choose your preferred Launcher from within the â€˜Applyâ€™ section within the Dashboard App to apply it to your home-screen. Enjoy!

New and Redesigned Icons
(Check the Icons > New section in the App)
